===展覽===

羅馬倫敦的重要考古發現，包括鑲嵌工藝、城牆瓦礫及古建築，曾藏於[[倫敦博物館|倫敦博物館]]及數間{{link-en|市政廳博物館|Guildhall_Museum}}（Guildhall Museum）。<ref name=oats>Hall & Merrifield.</ref> 1965年後匯合，<ref name="1965act">{{cite web|url=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1965/17/enacted|title=Museum of London Act 1965|work=legislation.gov.uk|publisher=National Archives|accessdate=26 February 2012|archive-date=2018-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828035619/http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1965/17/enacted|dead-url=no}}</ref>展於現今的倫敦博物館（近[[巴比肯藝術中心|巴比肯藝術中心]]）。一間以倫敦[[港口|港口]]歷史為主題的分館——{{link-en|倫敦港區博物館|Museum of London Docklands}}（Museum of London Docklands），2003年在[[道格斯島|道格斯島]]開幕。其他羅馬倫敦的考古發現，將由[[大英博物館|大英博物館]]繼續存放。<ref name=oats/>

城牆遺跡大部分屬於[[中世紀|中世紀]]，而[[羅馬帝國|羅馬時期]]一段在[[塔丘站|塔丘站]]附近、Coopers Row 8-10號一間酒店的庭院，以及Wood街旁邊的{{tsl|en|St Alphege London Wall||St Alphege Gardens}}都可以見到。<ref name=walle/> 有一段河堤可在[[倫敦塔|倫敦塔]]上眺望。<ref name=wallawalla>{{cite web|url=http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/02+riverside.htm|title=Londinium Today: Riverside wall|publisher=Museum of London Group|accessdate=17 February 2015|archive-date=2015-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822010706/http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/02+riverside.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[圓形競技場|圓形競技場]]的局部遺跡於{{link-en|市政廳藝廊|Guildhall Art Gallery}}（Guildhall Art Gallery）展出。<ref name=amp>{{cite web|url=http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/06+amphitheatre.htm|title=Londinium Today: The amphitheatre|publisher=Museum of London Group|accessdate=21 February 2015|archive-date=2015-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614013254/http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/06+amphitheatre.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 城西北的羅馬時期要塞，其西南塔樓仍可從Noble街見到。<ref name=foshow>{{cite web|url=http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/03+fort.htm|title=Londinium Today: The fort|publisher=Museum of London Group|accessdate=18 February 2015|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622183451/http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/03+fort.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 偶有羅馬時期遺跡納入了新建築地基的範圍，有待日後研究，但公眾一般無法造訪。<ref name=opwilldeliver>{{cite web|url=http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/04+forum.htm|title=Londinium Today: Basilica and forum|publisher=Museum of London Group|accessdate=19 February 2015|archive-date=2015-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616205346/http://archive.museumoflondon.org.uk/Londinium/Today/vizrom/04+forum.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=billybath/>

